<i>noun</i>: 평온 [평온], 적요 [저교], 적막감 [정막깜], 적막 [정막] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평온 [평온]</dt><br>
<dd>calmness; quietness; serenity</dd><br>
<dd>걱정이나 탈이 없고 조용함.</dd><br>
<dd>A quiet state without any worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>적요 [저교]</dt><br>
<dd>quietness</dd><br>
<dd>쓸쓸하고 고요함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being lonesome and silent.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>적막감 [정막깜]</dt><br>
<dd>1. loneliness; quietness</dd><br>
<dd>아무 소리 없이 조용하고 쓸쓸한 느낌이나 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>The feeling or state of being silent and lonesome with no sound being heard.</dd><br>
<dd>2. forlornness; loneliness</dd><br>
<dd>의지할 곳 없이 외로운 느낌이나 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>The feeling or state of being lonely with no one to depend on.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>적막 [정막]</dt><br>
<dd>1. quietness; silence</dd><br>
<dd>아무 소리 없이 조용하고 쓸쓸함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being silent and lonesome with no sound being heard.</dd><br>
<dd>2. forlornness</dd><br>
<dd>의지할 곳 없이 외로움.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being lonely with no one to depend on.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>